tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE LocationHistory (
    location_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    location TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ,
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES UserBehavior(user_id)
);

CREATE TABLE SuspiciousBehavior (
    behavior_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    behavior_description TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ,
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES UserBehavior(user_id)
);

CREATE TABLE BehaviorLogs (
   log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   user_id INT,
   location_id INT,
   log_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
   behavior_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE SecurityLogs (
   security_log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   user_id INT,
   location_id INT,
   log_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
   security_alert VARCHAR(200)
);
